### Practice Questions:

1. Find services that have admitted more than 500 patients in total.
2. Show services where average patient satisfaction is below 75.
3. List weeks where total staff presence across all services was less than 50.

### Daily Challenge:

**Question:** Identify services that refused more than 100 patients in total and had an average patient satisfaction below 80. Show service name, total refused, and average satisfaction.

***Queries

#1
select service, sum(patients_admitted)as Admit_total from services_weekly
group by service
having  Admit_total>500;

#2
select service, round(avg(patient_satisfaction), 0)as avg_sat from services_weekly
group by service
having  avg_sat < 75;

#3
select service, count(staff_name)as total from staff
group by service 
having total < 50;

#Challenge:

select 
   service,   
   sum(patients_refused) as total_refused,  
   round(avg(patient_satisfaction), 0 )as avg_satisfaction 
from services_weekly
group by service
having total_refused > 100 and avg_satisfaction < 80;



